These are Puzzles for 2x7 Level 1

.:: Puzzle 2x7-Level-1-1::.
The people perfer 7 different movie-genres: animation, thriller, scientific, western, spy, comedy, zombie
The people have 7 different hobbies: traveling, writing, gardening, board-games, drawing, baking, reading
 1. the person watching western movies is on the left of the person who's hobby is board-games##1
 2. the person who's hobby is drawing is the person watching western movies##1
 3. the person watching zombie movies is on the right of the person watching comedy movies##1
 4. the person who's hobby is gardening is on the right of the person who's hobby is baking##1
 5. the person watching scientific movies is in the middle##1
 6. the person who's hobby is traveling is on the far left##1
 7. the person watching spy movies is the person who's hobby is traveling##1
 8. the person watching animation movies is on the right of the person who's hobby is baking##1
 9. the person who's hobby is gardening is on the left of the person who's hobby is writing##1
10. the person who's hobby is board-games is on the left of the person watching scientific movies##1
11. the person watching zombie movies is on the right of the person who's hobby is writing##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |      1       |     2     |      3       |    4     |      5      |       6       |      7       |
| Movie-Genre           | spy | western | thriller | scientific | animation | comedy | zombie |
| Hobby   | traveling    | drawing   | board-games      | baking | gardening    | writing    | reading         |

