.:: Puzzle 2x7-Level-1-2::.
The people use 7 different means of transport: skateboard, bus, helicopter, jet-ski, quad-bike, tram, snowmobile
7 different pets are kept: goldfish, guinea-pig, lizard, goat, fish, pony, snake
 1. the owner of the fish is the person driving the jet-ski##1
 2. the person driving the tram is on the left of the owner of the snake##1
 3. the owner of the pony is on the far right##1
 4. the person driving the bus is on the right of the owner of the guinea-pig##1
 5. the person driving the jet-ski is on the right of the owner of the goat##1
 6. the person driving the tram is on the left of the person driving the snowmobile##1
 7. the owner of the fish is in the middle##1
 8. the owner of the fish is on the right of the person driving the quad-bike##1
 9. the owner of the snake is on the left of the person driving the helicopter##1
10. the person driving the jet-ski is on the left of the owner of the goldfish##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1     |    2     |   3   |     4     |     5     |     6      |    7     |
| Transport          | skateboard | bus | quad-bike | jet-ski | tram | snowmobile | helicopter |
| Pet   | guinea-pig      | lizard   | goat   | fish      | goldfish       | snake       | pony     |

