.:: Puzzle 2x7-Level-1-3::.
7 different pets are kept: goldfish, snake, frog, horse, hedgehog, hamster, cat
The people's birthday is in 7 different months: march, november, october, august, april, december, september
 1. the owner of the snake is on the left of the owner of the hedgehog##1
 2. the owner of the hedgehog is on the left of the person who's birthday is in september##1
 3. the person who's birthday is in november is on the left of the owner of the cat##1
 4. the owner of the goldfish is on the right of the owner of the hamster##1
 5. the person who's birthday is in march is the owner of the hedgehog##1
 6. the person who's birthday is in october is on the right of the person who's birthday is in november##1
 7. the person who's birthday is in november is on the left of the person who's birthday is in october##1
 8. the person who's birthday is in november is on the right of the person who's birthday is in august##1
 9. the owner of the hamster is the person who's birthday is in august##1
10. the owner of the frog is on the right of the person who's birthday is in march##1
11. the person who's birthday is in august is in the middle##1
12. the owner of the cat is on the left of the person who's birthday is in april##1

.:: Answer ::.
|        |    1     |     2     |   3    |      4       |     5      |    6     |     7     |
| Pet   | snake | hedgehog     | frog  | hamster       | goldfish       | cat  | horse   |
| Birthday    | december  | march | september | august | november | october | april |

