There are 7 different favourite colors: aquamarine, mauve, black, brown, blood-red, ebony, red
 1. the person traveling to hannover is the person who likes mauve##1
 2. the person traveling to boston is on the right of the person traveling to hamburg##1
 3. the person who likes ebony is on the right of the person who likes black##1
 4. the person who likes aquamarine is on the right of the person traveling to hannover##1
 5. the person traveling to hannover is on the left of the person traveling to prague##1
 6. the person traveling to hamburg is on the far left##1
 7. the person who likes black is on the right of the person traveling to hamburg##1
 8. the person traveling to liverpool is on the right of the person who likes ebony##1
 9. the person traveling to liverpool is the person who likes blood-red##1
10. the person who likes blood-red is on the left of the person traveling to edinburgh##1
11. the person who likes red is the person traveling to edinburgh##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |   1    |    2     |    3     |     4      |  5   |     6      |     7     |
| City   | hamburg    | boston     | colone     | liverpool      | edinburgh | hannover      | prague     |
| Color   | brown | black | ebony | blood-red | red | mauve | aquamarine |

