.:: Puzzle 2x7-Level-1-5::.
There are 7 different favourite beverages: milk, 7up, mirinda, soy-milk, lemonade, cola, fanta
The people prefer 7 different types of sport: ice-hockey, rowing, basketball, golf, biathlon, soccer, skateboarding
 1. the person drinking 7up is the person who's sport is skateboarding##1
 2. the person who's sport is rowing is on the right of the person drinking lemonade##1
 3. the person who's sport is soccer is in the middle##1
 4. the person who's sport is biathlon is on the right of the person who's sport is basketball##1
 5. the person who's sport is biathlon is the person drinking cola##1
 6. the person drinking lemonade is on the right of the person who's sport is ice-hockey##1
 7. the person who's sport is soccer is on the left of the person drinking fanta##1
 8. the person drinking mirinda is on the right of the person drinking 7up##1
 9. the person drinking soy-milk is on the right of the person who's sport is biathlon##1
10. the person drinking lemonade is on the right of the person drinking fanta##1

.:: Answer ::.
|         |    1    |    2    |     3      |     4     |      5      |      6       |      7      |
| Beverage   | 7up | mirinda | cola     | soy-milk | fanta | lemonade | milk |
| Sport     | skateboarding   | basketball    | biathlon | soccer     | ice-hockey         | golf     | rowing        |

