The people's birthday is in 7 different months: february, may, november, july, january, december, october
 1. the baccarat-smoker is on the left of the person who's birthday is in may##1
 2. the bolivar-smoker is on the left of the blend-smoker##1
 3. the bluemaster-smoker is the person who's birthday is in july##1
 4. the person who's birthday is in january is on the left of the davidoff-smoker##1
 5. the baccarat-smoker is on the right of the person who's birthday is in november##1
 6. the person who's birthday is in october is on the left of the person who's birthday is in november##1
 7. the person who's birthday is in february is the swisher-smoker##1
 8. the blend-smoker is in the middle##1
 9. the person who's birthday is in october is on the right of the bluemaster-smoker##1
10. the person who's birthday is in february is on the right of the davidoff-smoker##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |      2      |   3   |      4       |     5      |     6     |   7   |
| Cigar   | bongani  | bluemaster | bolivar | blend | baccarat     | davidoff | swisher |
| Birthday     | december | july      | october | november    | january | may   | february  |

