.:: Puzzle 2x7-Level-1-8::.
There are 7 different favourite beverages: soy-milk, juice, hot-chocolate, mirinda, sprite, 7up, coffee
There 7 different types of food: lemon, papaya, apple, onion, potato, pumpkin, raspberry
 1. the person drinking sprite is on the right of the person eating onion##1
 2. the person eating raspberry is in the middle##1
 3. the person drinking juice is the person eating apple##1
 4. the person eating apple is on the far left##1
 5. the person eating potato is on the right of the person eating onion##1
 6. the person drinking hot-chocolate is the person eating onion##1
 7. the person drinking 7up is on the left of the person eating papaya##1
 8. the person eating lemon is on the right of the person drinking mirinda##1
 9. the person drinking 7up is in the middle##1
10. the person drinking hot-chocolate is on the right of the person drinking soy-milk##1

.:: Answer ::.
|             |     1     |     2     |      3      |       4       |     5      |     6      |    7    |
