The people use 7 different means of transport: taxi, airplane, bike, car, boat, helicopter, bus
 1. the nigerian is the person driving the airplane##1
 2. the colombian is on the right of the person driving the taxi##1
 3. the colombian is on the left of the nigerian##1
 4. the russian is on the right of the british##1
 5. the british is on the far left##1
 6. the indonesian is on the left of the person driving the helicopter##1
 7. the person driving the airplane is on the right of the person driving the car##1
 8. the canadian is in the middle##1
 9. the indonesian is on the right of the person driving the boat##1
10. the person driving the bus is on the right of the russian##1

.:: Answer ::.
|        |     1      |     2     |   3    |     4      |     5      |     6      |    7     |
| Nationality   | british    | russian    | indonesian   | canadian | argentine | colombian | nigerian   |
| Transport    | bike | boat | bus | helicopter  | taxi       | car     | airplane |

